Description.BulletDescription:
[RAM & Storage] This computer comes with 12GB RAM | 1024GB SSD 
[AMD Ryzen 5 7530U Processor] It is a processor for thin and light laptops based on the Cezanne generation. It is part of the second "Barcelo" refresh in early 2023 and offers 200 MHz higher boost clock for the CPU cores compared to the old Ryzen 5 5625U . It integrates six of the eight cores based on the Zen 3 microarchitecture. The cores are clocked at 2 (guaranteed base clock) to 4.5 GHz (single core boost) and support SMT for a total of 12 threads.
